Title: The Gervais-Neveu-Felder equation and the quantum Calogero-Moser systems

Comments: Comments and References added

Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 178 (1996) 281-300

We quantize the spin Calogero-Moser model in the $R$-matrix formalism. Thequantum $R$-matrix of the model is dynamical. This $R$-matrix has alreadyappeared in Gervais-Neveu's quantization of Toda field theory and in Felder'squantization of the Knizhnik-Zamolodchikov-Bernard equation.